                  "DYNAM"
                ],
                "institute": "2GERBOC"
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The 450 Kv Single-Stage Accelerator and the 4 Mv Tandem",
                "Of the Dynamitron Tandem Laboratorium at the",
                "Ruhr-Universitat Bochum Provided Proton Beams at E = 75",
                "To 1800 KeV with Currents I = 200 Na (HIGH ENERGIES) To",
                "29 Mu-A (LOW ENERGIES) At the Target (LIMITED BY THE",
                "REQUIREMENT OF TARGET STABILITY AND BY DEAD-TIME",
                "EFFECTS IN THE Y-RAY DETECTOR).  The Energy Calibration",
                "Of the Accelerators was Tested During the Course of the",
                "Experiments Using the Well-Known 19-F(P,A)16-O",
                "Resonances at E = 224.0, 340.5, and 872.1 KeV and is",
                "Known to a Precision of +/- 0.5 KeV.  The Proton Energy",
                "Spread of Both Accelerators was Found to be Below 1.0",
                "KeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
