                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "  4-Pi Summing Crystal.",
                "The Capture Gamma-Rays were Observed Using a 12X12 Inch",
                "Nai(TL) Crystal with a Central Bore Hole of 35 mm",
                "Diameter and a 0.5 mm Al Wall Thickness."
              ]
            }
          ],
