          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Two Solid Targets were Used.  One Target was Produced",
                "By Evaporating About 6 Mu-G/Cm-Sq be-9 on a 0.5 mm",
                "Thick (CLEANED) Cu Backing.  This Target was Used in",
                "All Measurements (I.E.  EXCITATION FUNCTION AND",
                "ABSOLUTE CROSS SECTION), Due to Its Small Thickness  of",
                "1.1+/-0.2 KeV, Observed at the 1083 KeV Resonance in",
                "9 be(P,G)10-B.  For the Measurement of  Absolute  Cross",
                "Sections, Another Target Consisting of a 10",
                "Mu-G/Cm-Sq Thick be Layer on a 0.3 mm  Thick  (CLEANED)",
                "Ta Backing was Also Used, with an Observed Thickness of",
                "5.1+/-0.5 KeV at the 1083 KeV Resonance."
              ]
            }
          ],
